Roger - Hello, Uncle and Auntie,
Happy New Year!

33
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,200
Here’s a little present for you.
- You shouldn’t have

34
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,920
Do you live in Tin Shui Wai? So far away…

35
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,720
Have a seat

36
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:55,040
Let me get the steamed fish,
and dinner will be ready.

37
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,520
Have a seat - Sure, thank you.

38
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:00,240
Would you like to have some melon seeds?
- We are having dinner now!

39
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:07,320
Are you studying or working?

40
