104
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,680
I am still here

105
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:51,160
The doctor asked me…

106
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:04,000
He asked me what was our relationship

107
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,480
I did not know how to answer

108
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:11,800
I couldn’t take care of her in these critical times

109
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,440
Then I said as I was lying on the bed

110
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,480
Life Partner

111
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:27,640
I used to believe that only straight people have the right to marry

112
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:33,800
But today I know we also have that right

113
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:37,840
We can love each other like normal people

114
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,240
I hope they can have the freedom to choose…

115
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:43,320
I hope more people can have this kind of social recognition

116
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,080
It’s been 18 years already

117
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,920
We have been living together for a very long time

118
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:53,400
We think our relationship will enter another stage after marriage

119
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,240
I hope we won’t fight or break up over trivial things

120
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,880
I hope he won’t hit me anymore

121
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,720
My family know, they are all here

122
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:06,040
Please have tea, Dad

123
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:14,720
Family is very important to me and Roger

124
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,840
When I came out,
I only wanted to be with Roger

125
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:24,320
As time passed, there had been blessings
from friends and family on both sides…

126
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:28,000
