137
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:45,960
How are you feeling?

138
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,040
I, Roger Tsang,

139
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:27,040
take thee, Ricky Fung

140
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,440
to be my lawful husband

141
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,640
To have and to hold from this day forward,

142
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,760
for better, for worse,

143
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,040
for richer for poorer,

144
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,200
in sickness and in health,

145
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:46,680
according to Gods holy ordinance

146
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:49,920
to love

147
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:52,680
and cherish thee...

148
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,640
till death do us part

149
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:50,040
The love between us is not only recorded in photos on our phones

150
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:53,160
It also contains numerous frustrations that reinforce the bond between us

151
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:58,200
Whenever we faced challenges in our relationship, or if one person broke down,

152
00:18:58,720 --> 00:19:00,880
the other would be by his side

153
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:05,760
I mentioned my illness to many of my friends,

154
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:09,440
Every time it was like another coming-out. Sometimes I felt,

155
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:15,480
life is all about pushing door open, one after another,

156
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:18,880
coming out of closet after another

157
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:31,640
Thanks in advance, I will make an appointment to
