and you were overlooked

186
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:03,400
By the time we found out you were sick,
it was too late

187
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:11,120
Don’t be scared, I can still stand and walk,
I would always be here for you

188
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:49,000
Let me handle it

189
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:17,360
persistence,

190
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,600
It’s a kind of insistence,

191
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:23,760
a commitment to the other person
that kept us together

192
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:29,080
This persistence can be blind,
even unrealistic,

193
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:34,680
But allowed us to keep the relationship alive until now

194
